  ('Material UI', 'Frontend & Mobile', 'easy', 'Which component is a general layout/spacing primitive?', '["Box","Grid only","Paper only","Stack only"]'::jsonb, 0, 'Box is a versatile wrapper supporting the sx prop for styling.'),
