  ('Rspack', 'Frontend & Mobile', 'easy', 'What is Rspack?', '["A fast Rust-based bundler","A CSS framework","A JavaScript engine","A test runner"]'::jsonb, 0, 'Rspack is a high-performance bundler written in Rust.'),
  ('Rspack', 'Frontend & Mobile', 'easy', 'Which ecosystem is Rspack compatible with?', '["webpack''s config, loaders, and plugins","Rollup only","Vite plugins only","Gulp"]'::jsonb, 0, 'Rspack aims for webpack compatibility to ease migration.'),
  ('Rspack', 'Frontend & Mobile', 'easy', 'What language is Rspack written in?', '["Rust","Go","C#","JavaScript"]'::jsonb, 0, 'Rspack''s core is implemented in Rust for speed.'),
