  ('KQL', 'Monitoring', 'mid', 'What does summarize do?', '["Aggregates rows (count, avg, etc.) by groups","Sorts rows","Filters rows","Renames columns"]'::jsonb, 0, 'summarize computes aggregations, optionally grouped by keys.'),
